Shaon -- Perl Wiki with iPhone view

Please help me with development!

Require:
Dancer
DBIx::Simple
SQL::Abstract
URI::Escape
LWP::UserAgent
HTML::Entities
Text::Xatena
Cache::MemoryCache

Set up server:
Confer Dancer on CPAN (http://search.cpan.org/dist/Dancer/lib/Dancer/Deployment.pod)

This programme uses following libraries:
iWebKit (http://iwebkit.net/)